project
~~~~~~~

. Creates directories
. Shows created directories

main
~~~~

Use these variables.

  BASEDIR=$PROJECTOUTPUTDIR/$PROJECT
  BASERUNANALYSIS=$BASEDIR/run-analysis
  NUMBERDIR=$BASEDIR/$REPETITION
  DATADIR=$NUMBERDIR/data
  BWADIR=$NUMBERDIR/bwa
  RUNANALYSIS=$NUMBERDIR/run-analysis




